Lesotho lena le palo ya batho ba ka lekanyetswang hoba 2,067,000. Dipalopalo tsa batho ba Lesotho dika balwa ho diporesente tse 25% dibakeng tsa ditoropong,athe haele metseng le mahaeng ekaba diporesente tse kabang mashome a supileng le metso e mehlano.

